originalText.text: I've been looking for piano movers for a while and could not find anyone that was able to move my old large  piano to my new house. I found these guys online, they stopped by looked at it and my piano was moved the same day nice and smooth for a very reasonable price. Yes it took a lot of work but they were willing to do it, just wanted to say thank you.

originalText.text: Wonderful experience! The whole crew was friendly, efficient and very professional. I was able to get my baby grand moved from NJ to Manhattan for a very reasonable price. I strongly recommend Active Moving Inc.!

originalText.text: Awesome job! I thought for sure that my price was going to go up because everyoe warned me that it might happen and it never did. I paid what they said I was going to pay. I was really impressed with how the movers handled themselves. They worked hard and if they had any questions they asked instead of just assuming. I really appreciated their services!!

Hopefully it's just a piano-- but still be careful

This whole company needs to be shut down. The most unprofessional bunch of scam artists. The whole experience was and is a horror a story. From the quote given immediately changing, to the constant games with $$- promising of dates.. this goes on & on.  JUST DON'T USE THIS COMPANY IF YOU EVER WANT TO SEE YOUR STUFF- NEVER EVEN RECEIVED BELONGINGS.
The most unethical form of business that exists. They should be shut down.
